    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec BMW E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six. This unit features a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-equipped M-Variable differential lock for superior power delivery. Mechanical maintenance is up to date, including a proactive Double VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for chassis rigidity. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. A mechanically sound example ready for the twisties.",
