    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and performance, offering a reliable driving experience for its next owner. The exterior features the original factory paint, which retains a deep, lustrous shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood consistent with highway use, the body is straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is appointed with premium leather upholstery that remains soft and supple, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and navigation system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service history. It recently underwent a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection. The transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension remains firm and quiet over bumps. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, well-cared-for example that is ready for the road immediately.",
