      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! It runs like a dream and is super comfortable for those long drives. If you're looking for a reliable ride that still looks great, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
