    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit exhibits excellent compression and a recently recalibrated double-VANOS system, ensuring precise variable valve timing across the rev range. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement to address common floor pan fatigue, and the suspension retains its signature handling characteristics with refreshed bushings. While the exterior displays minor patina consistent with road use, the individual throttle bodies provide the immediate, linear throttle response that defines this era of M-power. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car ready for the apex.",
